{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3507030/extras/Leonardo_Phoenix_10_A_striking_logo_for_the_game_Zombie_Maraud_0__1_.jpg?t=1738736144\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Zombie Marauders is a minimalistic zombie time survival game with idle game mechanics. The zombies are all kinds of vicious and some even have magical powers. As the lone survivor, you have an arsenal of weapons to rip through hell's worst and make humanity's last stand!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3507030/extras/Default_A_dramatic_highcontrast_image_featuring_a_bold_distres_2_8d9c4be6-fa5c-4dec-b5b5-2eee5f622145_0.png?t=1738736144\" />Starting with a simple pistol, kill zombies to earn money, and unlock weapons and weapon upgrades. Try to survive as long as you can. Earn prestige in each playthrough to level up faster in subsequent attempts.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Starting Tips</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">1. Don't stay still. They will be on you from all directions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2. You don't have to upgrade all weapons. Pick those that match your playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3. Prioritize faster enemies and deal more damage to increase your chances of survival</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3507030/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738736144","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3507030/page.bg.jpg?t=1738736144","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3507030/5738386d807f7e426c9f15bef20df1a81b037b7a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738736144","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3507030/5738386d807f7e426c9f15bef20df1a81b037b7a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738736144","categ